rally be won over with food but cats are much tougher to convince. One of my three cat gurus accompanied me to every shoot and helped wrangle and cajole the subjects. Together we determined where the best place to shoot was, usually a compromise between where the cat was most comfortable and what seemed most aesthetically viable.” \u003c/p\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774065\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774065\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/08_Lucille-1.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/08_Lucille-1-530x800.jpg\" alt=\"A sitting tabby cat with bright yellow-green eyes, a mix of black, brown, and orange fur, and white paws and chest, against a neutral background.\" width=\"530\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/08_Lucille-1-530x800.jpg 530w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/08_Lucille-1-212x320.jpg 212w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/08_Lucille-1.jpg 663w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774065\"\u003eLucille\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774068\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774068\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/012_Wolfgang-2.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/012_Wolfgang-2-592x800.jpg\" alt=\"A fluffy, curly-haired cat with cream and orange fur looks upward against a black background. Its ears are perked, and its expression is curious.\" width=\"592\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/012_Wolfgang-2-592x800.jpg 592w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/012_Wolfgang-2-237x320.jpg 237w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/012_Wolfgang-2.jpg 740w