el.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/018_Mira-3.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/018_Mira-3-800x714.jpg\" alt=\"A fluffy, long-haired cat playfully bites and holds a thin stick with its paws against a black background, its mouth open in mid-snarl.\" width=\"800\" height=\"714\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/018_Mira-3-800x714.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/018_Mira-3-320x285.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/018_Mira-3-1536x1370.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/018_Mira-3.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774072\"\u003eMira\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/9781797228747.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/9781797228747-576x800.jpg\" alt=\"Close-up of a tabby cat with green eyes against a light background. The book cover text reads \u0026#34;Rescue Cats: Portraits and Stories\u0026#34; by Traer Scott.\" width=\"576\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/9781797228747-576x800.jpg 576w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/9781797228747-230x320.jpg 230w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/9781797228747.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eRescue Cats\u003c/em\u003e is published by Chronicle Books and available \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Rescue-Cats-Portraits-Traer-Scott/dp/1797228749?crid=1HVFOPZ1ZE23Q\u0026amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.RXw2TPVdFmMCXbFjISIv06-enjXjWJuMDgD83_7MAnu6klPJ5_NcjbQQPhPWBTU61LIqM9IO8MRVXc5VPVUxjIGcEjEeSSnc8hkYxVj-4RzV9N_Gn5S-9YzOVimyYEe4lBjZI4S2nc_rw8fqxhRT1LKLf7lXwvM-arMxr